  "reference_number": "MYA0011",
  "remarks": "\nBrigadier General Khin Hlaing, Commander of the Northeastern Command of the Myanmar Army. Responsible for serious human rights violations committed against the Rohingya population in Rakhine state, carried out by the 99th Light Infantry Division during his time as commander. These include unlawful killings, forced detainment, repression of the civilian population and systematic burning of Rohingya houses and buildings.",
